item.title: Palo Alto Jumps on Stronger-Than-Expected Forecast for 2026
item.description: Palo Alto Networks Inc. jumped on a stronger-than-expected annual forecast, as the company seeks to provide customers with a bundle of AI-enabled cybersecurity products to fend off attacks.
